---
const heroImage = "/images/print/primera-partida-campanella-hero.png";
const qrImage = "/images/print/reserva-campanella-qr-base.png";
const logoImage = "/images/FABLogo.png";
const fabWordmark = "/images/print/fab-logo-official-trimmed.png";
const qrUrl = "fabtcgcolombia.club/primera-partida";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Volante - Primera partida de Flesh and Blood</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="flyer" aria-label="Volante de invitación a Flesh and Blood">
      <section class="hero" aria-label="Adultos jugando cartas en una cafeteria">
        <img src={heroImage} alt="" />
        <div class="heroShade"></div>
        <div class="brandLockup">
          <img src={logoImage} alt="FAB Colombia" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content">
        <div class="intro">
          <p class="eyebrow">Sesión de introducción en Campanella Plaza</p>
          <div class="titleGrid">
            <div class="titleCopy">
              <h1>JUEGUE SU PRIMERA PARTIDA DE</h1>
              <p class="subtitle">Juego coleccionable de estrategia 1 vs 1.</p>
            </div>
            <img class="fabWordmark" src={fabWordmark} alt="Flesh and Blood" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="middleGrid">
          <section class="benefits" aria-label="Beneficios">
            <ul>
              <li>No necesita experiencia previa.</li>
              <li>Le prestamos todo lo necesario.</li>
              <li>Aprenda jugando una partida real.</li>
              <li>Grupos pequeños de máximo 4 personas.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <aside class="info" aria-label="Informacion de la sesion">
            <div class="infoRow infoRow--duration">
              <span>Duración aproximada</span>
              <strong>90 minutos</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="infoRow">
              <span>Fechas</span>
              <strong>Domingo 14, 21 y 28 de junio<br />10:00 AM</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="infoRow">
              <span>Lugar</span>
              <strong>Campanella Plaza<br />Cali, sector Pance</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="note">
              <strong>Importante</strong>
              <p>Contenido en inglés. Recomendado para mayores de 15 años.</p>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>

        <section class="cta" aria-label="Reserva">
          <div class="ctaText">
            <h2>Escanee el código QR para reservar un cupo.</h2>
            <p>Cupos limitados para mantener una experiencia guiada y cercana.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="qrBox" aria-label="Área para insertar código QR">
            <img src={qrImage} alt="Código QR para reservar un cupo" />
            <span>{qrUrl}</span>
          </div>
        </section>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <span>Organizado por FAB Colombia</span>
        <small>FAB Colombia no está afiliado con Legend Story Studios. Flesh and Blood™ es marca de Legend Story Studios®.</small>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  @page {
    size: Letter portrait;
    margin: 0;
  }

  :root {
    --ink: #f6efe4;
    --muted: #c8baaa;
    --paper: #16120f;
    --panel: #221b16;
    --panelSoft: #2c241e;
    --line: rgba(218, 181, 106, 0.38);
    --gold: #d7b26a;
    --goldSoft: #efd89e;
    --warmGray: #7f7468;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html,
  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100%;
    background: #3a342f;
    font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  body {
    display: grid;
    place-items: start center;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .flyer {
    position: relative;
    width: 8.5in;
    height: 11in;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 36%, rgba(197, 146, 71, 0.22), transparent 30%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #15100d 0%, #211913 48%, #120f0d 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 22px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .flyer::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0.2in;
    border: 1px solid rgba(215, 178, 106, 0.34);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 2.85in;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #17120f;
  }

  .hero img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    filter: saturate(0.95) contrast(1.08);
  }

  .heroShade {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 0%, rgba(20, 14, 10, 0.15) 42%, #15100d 100%),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42) 0%, transparent 34%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32) 100%);
  }

  .brandLockup {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.2in;
    left: 0.34in;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 1.25in;
    height: 1.25in;
    padding: 0.06in;
    background: rgba(10, 8, 7, 0.55);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
  }

  .brandLockup img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 0.25in 0.58in 0;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: none;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.08in;
    color: var(--goldSoft);
    font-size: 0.16in;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.31in;
    line-height: 1.02;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .titleGrid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2.25in) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 0.22in;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .titleCopy {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .fabWordmark {
    display: block;
    justify-self: end;
    width: 3.75in;
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    margin: -0.08in -0.03in -0.08in 0;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0.05in 0.1in rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55));
  }

  .subtitle {
    margin: 0.13in 0 0;
    color: var(--goldSoft);
    font-size: 0.215in;
    line-height: 1.16;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .middleGrid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: 0.34in;
    margin-top: 0.22in;
  }

  .benefits,
  .cta {
    background: rgba(29, 23, 18, 0.58);
  }

  .benefits {
    padding: 0.12in 0 0.04in;
  }

  .benefits ul {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.13in;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .benefits li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 0.27in;
    color: #f7efe4;
    font-size: 0.19in;
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .benefits li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.075in;
    width: 0.11in;
    height: 0.11in;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    background: rgba(215, 178, 106, 0.16);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .info {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.08in;
    padding: 0.11in 0 0;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .infoRow {
    padding-bottom: 0.075in;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(215, 178, 106, 0.24);
  }

  .infoRow--duration {
    padding-top: 0.02in;
  }

  .infoRow span,
  .note strong {
    display: block;
    color: #a99a88;
    font-size: 0.105in;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .infoRow strong {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.04in;
    color: #fff2dc;
    font-size: 0.18in;
    line-height: 1.14;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .note {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .note p {
    margin: 0.05in 0 0;
    color: #dfd3c1;
    font-size: 0.14in;
    line-height: 1.24;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .cta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.55in;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3in;
    margin-top: 0.24in;
    padding: 0.2in 0.26in;
    min-height: 1.75in;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(215, 178, 106, 0.35);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(215, 178, 106, 0.24);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(215, 178, 106, 0.14), rgba(29, 23, 18, 0.86) 48%),
      rgba(29, 23, 18, 0.72);
  }

  .cta h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #fff4df;
    font-size: 0.235in;
    line-height: 1.08;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .cta p {
    margin: 0.08in 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.145in;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .qrBox {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 1.55in;
    min-height: 1.68in;
    padding: 0.055in;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 0.055in solid #ffffff;
    outline: 1px solid rgba(215, 178, 106, 0.75);
    color: #211913;
  }

  .qrBox img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .qrBox span {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 0.03in;
    color: #211913;
    font-size: 0.058in;
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-align: center;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  footer {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.55in;
    right: 0.55in;
    bottom: 0.2in;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.025in;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 0;
    border-top: 0;
    color: var(--goldSoft);
    font-size: 0.105in;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  footer small {
    max-width: 6.7in;
    color: rgba(246, 239, 228, 0.58);
    font-size: 0.052in;
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: none;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
    body {
      padding: 0;
      place-items: start;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
  }

  @media print {
    html,
    body {
      width: 8.5in;
      height: 11in;
      background: white;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .flyer {
      box-shadow: none;
    }
  }
</style>
